{"tid":1380837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實好多公司都同員工簽下咗一份不得曠工罷工嘅合約。","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:37:27.000Z","uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ba8a920595ae601e6c0d46e59e78f550a9e7db34","tid":1380837,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友響南丫島做電， 佢哋一罷工，共成個港島區冇電。<br />\n雖然入面好多人都好支持呢樣嘢， 但係佢哋 簽曬合約 ，一罷工，公司可以即刻炒鳩咗你。 大把人渴望可以頂上。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一班公務員， 佢哋只能夠 以個人名義去偷偷表達， 好難去做到集體罷工。<br />\n因為有政治立場，都係會違反咗公務員守則， 影響成個公務員團隊，都係隨時可以炒佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係響入面高薪厚職嗰班， 年年都有人想坐佢哋個位， 佢哋真係老閪都唔會罷工。 更加唔會容許佢哋嘅屬下隨便罷工。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一班打工仔， 大部分香港人有穩定職業嘅人都孭咗層樓響身， 若果份工出咗乜嘢事， 供樓嗰度就好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢哋再支持班後生仔都好， 都未必會真係同你哋罷工。<br />\n<br />\n唔係想散播失敗主義，但若果真係咁簡單嘅話民陣之前六月，曾經發起過兩次罷工，一早已經有好多人響應啦。<br />\n就係叫咗出嚟都冇效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n另外之前都好多人講， 罷工究竟係一日就完定係好多日，一路咁落去。<br />\n8月5一日就完既話，之前我地都屌民陣根本上就攞唔到嗰個效果。 有期限嘅罷工 係 只係等於一個星期日或者係公眾假期， 打工仔只會損失一日年假去幫你， 但完全收唔到想要嘅效果，政府亦都唔會驚你。<br />\n<br />\n唔信嘅話，你哋自己睇清楚個結果係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3097a4a45b4d980d0dceffc78721f205f6ef4f20","tid":1380837,"uid":51848,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PddP7ro.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPddP7ro.png&h=cf398dc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9159a180e41812a674fca86eb15cc23952b2cd7","tid":1380837,"uid":192697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"病左唔識請病假？"},{"pid":"f4db17fe2861ffdf94922120c45aa3c8427ec10c","tid":1380837,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:20:17.000Z","msg":"黑警紮職當初都話要保護市民"},{"pid":"adafe113d9a5843856415d81c8078cb598cfe322","tid":1380837,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9159a180e41812a674fca86eb15cc23952b2cd7","tid":1380837,"uid":192697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"病左唔識請病假？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:39:44.000Z","msg":"得，但集體請管理層就要做野， 同埋你唔知佢將會幾時做嘢"},{"pid":"de6af7280fd57564dec3fad260f3e9752803c991","tid":1380837,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"唔係你份約話乜就乜，唔跟勞工條例既你白字黑字簽多10個名都無用"},{"pid":"d482d80fe32d722a89e11d26af1a5a0feb4c215e","tid":1380837,"uid":263174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"所以罷工日應該搞不合作運動"},{"pid":"41b21544e96318e319189d4904d649c8b96ad9de","tid":1380837,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"de6af7280fd57564dec3fad260f3e9752803c991","tid":1380837,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"唔係你份約話乜就乜，唔跟勞工條例既你白字黑字簽多10個名都無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"人哋可以用曠工出警告信或者按勞工法例 炒撚咗你。<br />\n你可以罷幾多日工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你不如問下有幾多公務員真係會響應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成件事唔好諗到咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民陣都講咗好多次都搞唔成"},{"pid":"8cef97b1a28e7db500d686e4364591d5bdebc1f9","tid":1380837,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d482d80fe32d722a89e11d26af1a5a0feb4c215e","tid":1380837,"uid":263174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"所以罷工日應該搞不合作運動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"塞左咁多次鐵，你覺得點？有幾多人響應。"},{"pid":"a0d09734a272bf0f4a99e6da588c6bff9c3ce23f","tid":1380837,"uid":60563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir黃左咁耐仲咁努力係度洗地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc83b85b8b2fadd99585bc5f2484e31c7af4b60","tid":1380837,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a0d09734a272bf0f4a99e6da588c6bff9c3ce23f","tid":1380837,"uid":60563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir黃左咁耐仲咁努力係度洗地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"我係撚警察咩， 查清楚先啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個都知我極度反警喇"},{"pid":"80b49fa0e7c56d8858b1124c40954539f71adb99","tid":1380837,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8812dfed4b343a021e8d4192f57f25b91349f7ff","tid":1380837,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}